Paper: hep-th/0111122

Date: 2001-11-13

Title: Covariant Coordinate Transformations on Noncommutative Space

Authors: R. Jackiw and S.-Y. Pi

Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX; email correspondence to jackiw@lns.mit.edu

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 88 (2002) 111603

We show how to define gauge-covariant coordinate transformations on anoncommuting space. The construction uses the Seiberg-Witten equation andgeneralizes similar results for commuting coordinates.